Text: Is this another torrent stuck at 99.8%? hope not...
Extremely good audio quality. However, the complete files are not available; the end of Tears and start of Something for Nothing are nowhere to be found.

Awesome that this was from vinyl. I liked the occasional snap crackle pop. Great to hear this album again. I didn't mind Tears stopping a little short; couldn't play Something for Nothing but no big deal. Alex Lifeson's ballsack.
